on the PSP. How sad that my all-time favorite console game is getting a bunch of spiffy new features on a handheld I chose not to support. =(
At least we are getting a Dragon Quest release for the DS.

A friend of mine at work once commented to me that I ask the silliest questions.
When I&rsquo;m a bit bored at the office, I will sometimes throw random meaning-of-life questions at them. things like:
&ldquo;If you had a time machine, what would you do with it?&rdquo;
&ldquo;IF you were president, what would you do about [thing]?&rdquo;
&ldquo;What&rsquo;s your most impossible dream?&rdquo;
&ldquo;If you could vanish right now, where would you go?
